About the oberoi
Set on perfectly manicured grounds about six kilometres from Bengaluru Palace, The Oberoi Bangalore is a luxurious 5-star hotel featuring a 24-hour butler service and fully fitted gym.
Elegantly decorated rooms are air-conditioned and feature private balconies with magnificent views. An iPad interface means movies, lighting, and so much more is just the touch of a button away.
First-class services and facilities include, amongst others, a rejuvenating spa with massages and steam baths, and a stunning pool set outdoors amidst the lush vegetation.
